---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sol si Apa — Cercetare RAIDAVA">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-green-primary text-white py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-4 tracking-tight">Sol si Apa</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-heading font-medium text-cream-dark">Fundatia oricarei ferme regenerative</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cadrul Geologic -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-green-primary mb-8 text-center">Cadrul Geologic</h2>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-cream-dark">
        <div class="space-y-4 text-green-primary/80 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Vulturesti se afla in <span class="font-semibold text-green-primary">zona de contact intre Piemontul Getic si Campia Romana</span>,
            o pozitie geologica privilegiata care ofera o diversitate remarcabila de soluri si forme de relief pe o suprafata compacta.
          </p>
          <p>
            In lunca Argesului se gasesc <span class="font-semibold text-green-primary">depozite aluviale recente</span> — sedimente
            transportate si depuse de apa pe parcursul mileniilor, creand unele dintre cele mai fertile soluri din zona.
          </p>
          <p>
            Substratul geologic este alcatuit din <span class="font-semibold text-green-primary">argile, nisipuri si pietrish</span>,
            o combinatie care asigura atat retentia apei cat si drenajul natural — conditii excelente pentru radacinile plantelor.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mozaicul Pedologic -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-green-primary mb-8 text-center">Mozaicul Pedologic</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-green-primary/70 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Diversitatea de soluri din zona Vulturesti permite alocarea strategica a fiecarui tip de cultura pe solul optim.
      </p>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-green-primary text-white">
              <th class="font-heading font-semibold text-left px-4 py-3 text-sm">Zona Relief</th>
              <th class="font-heading font-semibold text-left px-4 py-3 text-sm">Tip Sol</th>
              <th class="font-heading font-semibold text-left px-4 py-3 text-sm">Caracteristici</th>
              <th class="font-heading font-semibold text-left px-4 py-3 text-sm">Potrivire RAIDAVA</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-sm">
            <tr class="border-b border-cream-dark bg-cream">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">Lunca inundabila</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">Aluviosoluri</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-green-primary/70">Fertile, bine drenate, bogate in minerale</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">
                <span class="inline-block bg-green-secondary/10 text-green-secondary px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium">Culturi furajere</span>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-cream-dark">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">Terasa joasa</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">Cernoziomuri</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-green-primary/70">Humus bogat, pH neutru, textura echilibrata</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">
                <span class="inline-block bg-green-secondary/10 text-green-secondary px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium">Pasune, legume</span>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-cream-dark bg-cream">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">Versanti</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">Luvosoluri</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-green-primary/70">Argiloase, usor acide, retentie buna de apa</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">
                <span class="inline-block bg-brown-earth/10 text-brown-earth px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium">Livada, padure alimentara</span>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">Interfluvii</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">Preluvosoluri</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-green-primary/70">Fertilitate moderata, bine structurate</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">
                <span class="inline-block bg-brown-light/10 text-brown-light px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium">Cereale, cover crops</span>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Resurse de Apa -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-green-primary mb-8 text-center">Resurse de Apa</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-cream-dark">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg mb-3 text-green-secondary">Apa Subterana</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-primary/70 mb-3">
            Panza freatica se gaseste la <span class="font-semibold text-green-primary">2-8 metri</span> adancime in zona luncii,
            accesibila prin puturi simple. Nivelul variaza sezonier, fiind mai aproape de suprafata primavara.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-cream-dark">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg mb-3 text-green-secondary">Apa de Suprafata</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-primary/70 mb-3">
            Raul Arges se afla la aproximativ <span class="font-semibold text-green-primary">5 km</span> distanta.
            Exista posibilitatea amenajarii unui <span class="font-semibold text-green-primary">iaz de colectare</span> a
            apei pluviale pentru irigatie suplimentara si acvacultura.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-cream-dark">
        <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg mb-4 text-center text-green-secondary">
          Precipitatii Medii Lunare — 734 mm/an
        </h3>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full border-collapse text-center text-sm">
            <thead>
              <tr class="bg-green-primary text-white">
                <th class="px-2 py-2 font-heading font-semibold">Ian</th>
                <th class="px-2 py-2 font-heading font-semibold">Feb</th>
                <th class="px-2 py-2 font-heading font-semibold">Mar</th>
                <th class="px-2 py-2 font-heading font-semibold">Apr</th>
                <th class="px-2 py-2 font-heading font-semibold">Mai</th>
                <th class="px-2 py-2 font-heading font-semibold">Iun</th>
                <th class="px-2 py-2 font-heading font-semibold">Iul</th>
                <th class="px-2 py-2 font-heading font-semibold">Aug</th>
                <th class="px-2 py-2 font-heading font-semibold">Sep</th>
                <th class="px-2 py-2 font-heading font-semibold">Oct</th>
                <th class="px-2 py-2 font-heading font-semibold">Noi</th>
                <th class="px-2 py-2 font-heading font-semibold">Dec</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="bg-cream">
                <td class="px-2 py-3 font-medium">38</td>
                <td class="px-2 py-3 font-medium">36</td>
                <td class="px-2 py-3 font-medium">43</td>
                <td class="px-2 py-3 font-medium">58</td>
                <td class="px-2 py-3 font-medium text-green-secondary font-bold">82</td>
                <td class="px-2 py-3 font-medium text-green-secondary font-bold">95</td>
                <td class="px-2 py-3 font-medium text-green-secondary font-bold">78</td>
                <td class="px-2 py-3 font-medium">62</td>
                <td class="px-2 py-3 font-medium">52</td>
                <td class="px-2 py-3 font-medium">48</td>
                <td class="px-2 py-3 font-medium">52</td>
                <td class="px-2 py-3 font-medium">46</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="text-xs text-green-primary/50">
                <td class="px-2 py-1" colspan="12">Valori in mm. Lunile cu precipitatii peste 70 mm sunt evidentiate.</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Implicatii RAIDAVA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-green-primary mb-8 text-center">Implicatii pentru RAIDAVA</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-green-secondary">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Lunca Aluviala</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-primary/70">
            Solul aluvial din lunca este <span class="font-semibold text-green-primary">ideal pentru topinambur si lucerna</span> —
            doua culturi cheie in sistemul furajer al fermei. Fertilitatea naturala elimina nevoia de amendamente costisitoare.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-green-light">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Precipitatii Suficiente</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-primary/70">
            Cu 734 mm/an, <span class="font-semibold text-green-primary">precipitatiile acopera necesarul de apa fara irigatie</span>
            pentru majoritatea culturilor planificate. Distributia favorabila in sezonul de crestere este un avantaj major.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-brown-earth">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Versanti pentru Livada</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-primary/70">
            <span class="font-semibold text-green-primary">Zona de versant este ideala pentru livada traditionala</span> si
            padure alimentara. Luvosolurile argiloase sustin bine pomii fructiferi si arbustii.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
